aled in 12CO (3-2), together with the central\ndepression of the dust disk, may be explained to be driven by the possible\nexistence of a giant planet forming in the disk.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2006 06:33:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
