lude data as far out in the galactic disk as the observations\npresented here. A fit to published PDR models yields a plausible average\nsolution of G_0~100 and n~3000 for the PDR emission in the regions of star\nformation in the arm of M31.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 16 Mar 2006 14:42:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
