or the braneworld model. Further work on lensing\ntests of braneworld gravity must proceed into the physical optics regime, which\nawaits a description of the full spacetime geometry around braneworld black\nholes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 15 Mar 2006 18:12:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 10 May 2006 18:53:00 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 25 May 2006 20:53:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-11"}
